176
00:11:51.236 --> 00:11:54.206
I’m talking about you here.
Junior. Only you.

177
00:11:54.206 --> 00:11:55.878
What...?

178
00:11:55.878 --> 00:11:58.683
These tests require
real physical strength.

179
00:11:58.683 --> 00:12:01.246
