I just say no. right?

190
00:12:28.339 --> 00:12:30.110
If I just refuse.

191
00:12:30.110 --> 00:12:31.749
What happens then?

192
00:12:33.245 --> 00:12:36.050
You do know about conscription?

193
00:12:36.050 --> 00:12:37.348
During the old wars.

194
00:12:37.348 --> 00:12:39.383
