that nothing will be decided

220
00:13:48.793 --> 00:13:49.959
for a couple of years.

221
00:13:49.959 --> 00:13:51.323
A couple of years?

222
00:13:51.323 --> 00:13:53.160
Yeah. sadly.
these tests

223
00:13:53.160 --> 00:13:54.799
