226
00:14:00.266 --> 00:14:03.170
Yes. Because it is.

227
00:14:04.237 --> 00:14:06.008
Nothing’s been decided yet.

228
00:14:07.141 --> 00:14:08.373
Mm-hm.

229
00:14:23.520 --> 00:14:26.160
You look after that
wee Henrietta for me.

230
00:14:27.832 --> 00:14:29.900
